official_title: A bill to establish the Saint Marks National Wilderness Area in the State of Florida.

summary.text: Establishes the Saint Marks National Wilderness Area in the State of Florida. Provides that such wilderness area shall be administered by the Secretary of the Interior in accordance with the provisions of the Wilderness Act.

titles.title: A bill to establish the Saint Marks National Wilderness Area in the State of Florida.
